create using HTML, CSS, java script a Roll The Dice app. 
Back ground color as Dark Brown Transient 
First option would be to select the Dice Type (in mustard yellow color) with the default as D6. The drop down section in pale yellow.
Second option to select Dice Count (in mustard yellow color) with the default as 2. The drop down section in pale yellow.
Add two button Roll and Clear. Both are Yellow with the Inside Text in Dark Brown. 
Click on Roll will generate the result as random numbers based on the Dice Type and Dice Count showing in separate boxes 
the number of boxes for the result will be based on the Dice Count. Also the use a ligther color inside for the result numbers.
Clear Button - will clear the result
Display the sum of the numbers in the result and display as Total followed by the box with the sum.